lyrics.title: That's Rich
lyrics.content: Take your mirror off the wall Ain't you gettin' bored of your reflection? Now you want me? 'Cause I don't need a lazy lover Now you want me? No, I don't wanna meet your mother Now you want me? Don't cry, I'm sure you'll meet another And you'll tell her you love her Well that's rich When it's coming from you And that's rich Well I know all of your moves That's rich You think I dressed up for you And thаt'ѕ rich Bye bye fool Bye bye fool Bye bye fool Bye bye fool Bye bye fool Bye bye fool
